{
  "video_id": "zI0_fSD6GPY",
  "title": "Guy-Philippe Goldstein: How cyberattacks threaten real-world peace",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Elisabeth Buffard Reviewer: Veronica Martinez Starnes"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15260.0,
      "end_time": 16259.0,
      "text": "Good afternoon."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 16260.000000000002,
      "end_time": 18260.0,
      "text": "If you have followed"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 18260.0,
      "end_time": 20260.0,
      "text": "diplomatic news in the past weeks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 20260.0,
      "end_time": 22260.0,
      "text": "you may have heard of a kind of crisis"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 22260.0,
      "end_time": 24260.0,
      "text": "between China and the U.S."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 24260.0,
      "end_time": 26260.0,
      "text": "regarding cyberattacks"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 26260.0,
      "end_time": 28260.0,
      "text": "against the American company Google."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 28260.0,
      "end_time": 30260.0,
      "text": "Many things have been said about this."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 30260.0,
      "end_time": 32260.0,
      "text": "Some people have called a cyberwar"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 32259.0,
      "end_time": 34260.0,
      "text": "what may actually be"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 34260.0,
      "end_time": 36260.0,
      "text": "just a spy operation --"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 36260.0,
      "end_time": 38260.0,
      "text": "and obviously, a quite mishandled one."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 38260.0,
      "end_time": 41260.0,
      "text": "However, this episode reveals"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 41260.0,
      "end_time": 43260.0,
      "text": "the growing anxiety in the Western world"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 43260.0,
      "end_time": 46260.0,
      "text": "regarding these emerging cyber weapons."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 46260.0,
      "end_time": 48260.0,
      "text": "It so happens that these weapons are dangerous."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 48260.0,
      "end_time": 50260.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re of a new nature:"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 50260.0,
      "end_time": 52260.0,
      "text": "they could lead the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 52260.0,
      "end_time": 54260.0,
      "text": "into a digital conflict"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 54260.0,
      "end_time": 56260.0,
      "text": "that could turn into an armed struggle."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 56260.0,
      "end_time": 60260.0,
      "text": "These virtual weapons can also destroy the physical world."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 61260.0,
      "end_time": 64259.0,
      "text": "In 1982, in the middle of the Cold War"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 64260.00000000001,
      "end_time": 66260.0,
      "text": "in Soviet Siberia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 66260.0,
      "end_time": 70260.0,
      "text": "a pipeline exploded with a burst of 3 kilotons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 70260.0,
      "end_time": 72260.0,
      "text": "the equivalent of a fourth of the Hiroshima bomb."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 72260.0,
      "end_time": 74260.0,
      "text": "Now we know today -- this was revealed"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 74260.0,
      "end_time": 76260.0,
      "text": "by Thomas Reed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 76260.0,
      "end_time": 78260.0,
      "text": "Ronald Reagan&#39;s former U.S. Air Force Secretary --"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 78260.0,
      "end_time": 81260.0,
      "text": "this explosion was actually the result"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 81260.0,
      "end_time": 83260.0,
      "text": "of a CIA sabotage operation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 83260.0,
      "end_time": 85260.0,
      "text": "in which they had managed"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 85260.0,
      "end_time": 87260.0,
      "text": "to infiltrate the IT management systems"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 87260.0,
      "end_time": 89260.0,
      "text": "of that pipeline."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 89260.0,
      "end_time": 92260.0,
      "text": "More recently, the U.S. government revealed"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 92260.0,
      "end_time": 95260.0,
      "text": "that in September 2008, more than 3 million people"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 95260.0,
      "end_time": 98260.0,
      "text": "in the state of Espirito Santo in Brazil"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 98260.0,
      "end_time": 100260.0,
      "text": "were plunged into darkness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 100260.0,
      "end_time": 105260.0,
      "text": "victims of a blackmail operation from cyber pirates."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 105260.0,
      "end_time": 107260.0,
      "text": "Even more worrying for the Americans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 107260.0,
      "end_time": 110260.0,
      "text": "in December 2008 the holiest of holies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 110260.0,
      "end_time": 112260.0,
      "text": "the IT systems of CENTCOM,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 112260.0,
      "end_time": 114260.0,
      "text": "the central command"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 114260.0,
      "end_time": 117260.0,
      "text": "managing the wars in Iraq and Afghanistan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 117260.0,
      "end_time": 119260.0,
      "text": "may have been infiltrated by hackers"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 119260.0,
      "end_time": 122260.0,
      "text": "who used these:"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 122260.0,
      "end_time": 124260.0,
      "text": "plain but infected USB keys."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 124260.0,
      "end_time": 126260.0,
      "text": "And with these keys, they may have been able"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 126260.0,
      "end_time": 128259.0,
      "text": "to get inside CENTCOM&#39;s systems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 128258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 130258.99999999999,
      "text": "to see and hear everything,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 130258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 132260.0,
      "text": "and maybe even infect some of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 132260.0,
      "end_time": 134260.0,
      "text": "As a result, the Americans take the threat very seriously."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 134260.0,
      "end_time": 136260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll quote General James Cartwright,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 136260.0,
      "end_time": 138260.0,
      "text": "Vice Chairman of the Joint Chiefs of Staff,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 138260.0,
      "end_time": 140260.0,
      "text": "who says in a report to Congress"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 140260.0,
      "end_time": 143260.0,
      "text": "that cyberattacks could be as powerful as"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 143260.0,
      "end_time": 146260.0,
      "text": "weapons of mass destruction."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 146260.0,
      "end_time": 148260.0,
      "text": "Moreover, the Americans have decided"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 148260.0,
      "end_time": 150260.0,
      "text": "to spend over 30 billion dollars"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 150260.0,
      "end_time": 151760.0,
      "text": "in the next five years"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 151760.0,
      "end_time": 153260.0,
      "text": "to build up their cyberwar capabilities."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 154260.0,
      "end_time": 156260.0,
      "text": "And across the world today, we see"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 156260.0,
      "end_time": 159260.0,
      "text": "a sort of cyber arms race,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 159260.0,
      "end_time": 161260.0,
      "text": "with cyberwar units"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 161260.0,
      "end_time": 163260.0,
      "text": "built up by countries like North Korea"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 163260.0,
      "end_time": 164260.0,
      "text": "or even Iran."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 164260.0,
      "end_time": 166260.0,
      "text": "Yet, what you&#39;ll never hear"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 166260.0,
      "end_time": 168260.0,
      "text": "from spokespeople"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 168260.0,
      "end_time": 171260.0,
      "text": "from the Pentagon or the French Department of Defence"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 171260.0,
      "end_time": 173260.0,
      "text": "is that the question isn&#39;t really"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 173260.0,
      "end_time": 175260.0,
      "text": "who&#39;s the enemy, but actually"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 175260.0,
      "end_time": 178260.0,
      "text": "the very nature of cyber weapons."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 178260.0,
      "end_time": 180260.0,
      "text": "And to understand why, we must look at how,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 180260.0,
      "end_time": 183260.0,
      "text": "through the ages, military technologies"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 183260.0,
      "end_time": 185260.0,
      "text": "have maintained or destroyed"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 185260.0,
      "end_time": 187260.0,
      "text": "world peace."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 188260.0,
      "end_time": 190260.0,
      "text": "For example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 190260.0,
      "end_time": 191260.0,
      "text": "if we&#39;d had TEDxParis"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 191260.0,
      "end_time": 193260.0,
      "text": "350 years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 193260.0,
      "end_time": 196260.0,
      "text": "we would have talked about the military innovation of the day --"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 196260.0,
      "end_time": 199260.0,
      "text": "the massive Vauban-style fortifications --"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 199260.0,
      "end_time": 201260.0,
      "text": "and we could have predicted"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 201260.0,
      "end_time": 204260.0,
      "text": "a period of stability in the world or in Europe."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 204260.0,
      "end_time": 207260.0,
      "text": "which was indeed the case in Europe"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 207260.0,
      "end_time": 209260.0,
      "text": "between 1650 and 1750."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 209260.0,
      "end_time": 212260.0,
      "text": "Similarly, if we&#39;d had this talk"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 212260.0,
      "end_time": 215260.0,
      "text": "30 or 40 years ago, we would have seen"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 215260.0,
      "end_time": 217260.0,
      "text": "how the rise of nuclear weapons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 217260.0,
      "end_time": 221260.0,
      "text": "and the threat of mutually assured destruction they imply,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 221260.0,
      "end_time": 224260.0,
      "text": "prevents a direct fight between the two superpowers."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 225260.0,
      "end_time": 227260.0,
      "text": "However, if we&#39;d had this talk 60 years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 227260.0,
      "end_time": 230260.0,
      "text": "we would have seen how the emergence"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 230260.0,
      "end_time": 233260.0,
      "text": "of new aircraft and tank technologies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 233260.0,
      "end_time": 236260.0,
      "text": "which give the advantage to the attacker,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 236260.0,
      "end_time": 239260.0,
      "text": "make the Blitzkrieg doctrine very credible"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 239260.0,
      "end_time": 242260.0,
      "text": "and thus create the possibility of war in Europe."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 242260.0,
      "end_time": 244260.0,
      "text": "So military technologies"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 244260.0,
      "end_time": 246260.0,
      "text": "can influence the course of the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 246260.0,
      "end_time": 248260.0,
      "text": "can make or break world peace --"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 248260.0,
      "end_time": 250260.0,
      "text": "and there lies the issue with cyber weapons."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 250260.0,
      "end_time": 252260.0,
      "text": "The first issue:"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 252260.0,
      "end_time": 255260.0,
      "text": "Imagine a potential enemy announcing"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 255260.0,
      "end_time": 257260.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re building a cyberwar unit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 257260.0,
      "end_time": 259260.0,
      "text": "but only for their country&#39;s defense."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 259260.0,
      "end_time": 262260.0,
      "text": "Okay, but what distinguishes it"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 262260.0,
      "end_time": 264260.0,
      "text": "from an offensive unit?"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 264260.0,
      "end_time": 266260.0,
      "text": "It gets even more complicated"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 266260.0,
      "end_time": 270260.0,
      "text": "when the doctrines of use become ambiguous."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 270260.0,
      "end_time": 274260.0,
      "text": "Just 3 years ago, both the U.S. and France"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 274260.0,
      "end_time": 278260.0,
      "text": "were saying they were investing militarily in cyberspace,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 278260.0,
      "end_time": 280260.0,
      "text": "strictly to defend their IT systems."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 281260.0,
      "end_time": 284260.0,
      "text": "But today both countries say"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 284260.0,
      "end_time": 286260.0,
      "text": "the best defense is to attack."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 286260.0,
      "end_time": 288260.0,
      "text": "And so, they&#39;re joining China,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 288260.0,
      "end_time": 292260.0,
      "text": "whose doctrine of use for 15 years has been"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 292260.0,
      "end_time": 295260.0,
      "text": "both defensive and offensive."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 295260.0,
      "end_time": 297260.0,
      "text": "The second issue:"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 297260.0,
      "end_time": 301260.0,
      "text": "Your country could be under cyberattack"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 301260.0,
      "end_time": 304260.0,
      "text": "with entire regions plunged into total darkness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 304260.0,
      "end_time": 306260.0,
      "text": "and you may not even know"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 306260.0,
      "end_time": 308260.0,
      "text": "who&#39;s attacking you."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 308260.0,
      "end_time": 310600.0,
      "text": "Cyber weapons have this peculiar feature:"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 310600.0,
      "end_time": 311560.0,
      "text": "they can be used"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 311560.0,
      "end_time": 313260.0,
      "text": "without leaving traces."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 313260.0,
      "end_time": 315260.0,
      "text": "This gives a tremendous advantage to the attacker,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 315260.0,
      "end_time": 317260.0,
      "text": "because the defender"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 317260.0,
      "end_time": 319260.0,
      "text": "doesn&#39;t know who to fight back against."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 319260.0,
      "end_time": 321260.0,
      "text": "And if the defender retaliates against the wrong adversary,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 321260.0,
      "end_time": 324260.0,
      "text": "they risk making one more enemy"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 324260.0,
      "end_time": 326260.0,
      "text": "and ending up diplomatically isolated."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 326260.0,
      "end_time": 328260.0,
      "text": "This issue isn&#39;t just theoretical."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 328260.0,
      "end_time": 330260.0,
      "text": "In May 2007, Estonia was the victim of cyberattacks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 330260.0,
      "end_time": 333260.0,
      "text": "that damaged its communication"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 333260.0,
      "end_time": 335260.0,
      "text": "and banking systems."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 335260.0,
      "end_time": 337260.0,
      "text": "Estonia accused Russia."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 337260.0,
      "end_time": 339260.0,
      "text": "But NATO, though it defends Estonia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 339260.0,
      "end_time": 341260.0,
      "text": "reacted very prudently. Why?"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 341260.0,
      "end_time": 343260.0,
      "text": "Because NATO couldn&#39;t be 100% sure"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 343260.0,
      "end_time": 348260.0,
      "text": "that the Kremlin was indeed behind these attacks."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 348260.0,
      "end_time": 351260.0,
      "text": "So to sum up, on the one hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 351260.0,
      "end_time": 353260.0,
      "text": "when a possible enemy announces"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 353260.0,
      "end_time": 355260.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re building a cyberwar unit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 355260.0,
      "end_time": 357260.0,
      "text": "you don&#39;t know whether it&#39;s for attack"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 357260.0,
      "end_time": 358260.0,
      "text": "or defense."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 358260.0,
      "end_time": 359260.0,
      "text": "On the other hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 359260.0,
      "end_time": 363260.0,
      "text": "we know that these weapons give an advantage to attacking."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 363260.0,
      "end_time": 366260.0,
      "text": "In a major article published in 1978,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 366260.0,
      "end_time": 368260.0,
      "text": "Professor Robert Jervis of Columbia University in New York"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 368260.0,
      "end_time": 370260.0,
      "text": "described a model to understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 370260.0,
      "end_time": 372260.0,
      "text": "how conflicts could arise."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 372260.0,
      "end_time": 375260.0,
      "text": "In this context,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 375260.0,
      "end_time": 377260.0,
      "text": "when you don&#39;t know if the potential enemy"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 377260.0,
      "end_time": 380260.0,
      "text": "is preparing for defense or attack,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 380260.0,
      "end_time": 382260.0,
      "text": "and if the weapons give an advantage to attacking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 382260.0,
      "end_time": 384260.0,
      "text": "then this environment is"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 384260.0,
      "end_time": 388260.0,
      "text": "most likely to spark a conflict."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 388260.0,
      "end_time": 390260.0,
      "text": "This is the environment that&#39;s being created"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 390260.0,
      "end_time": 392260.0,
      "text": "by cyber weapons today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 392260.0,
      "end_time": 395260.0,
      "text": "and historically it was the environment in Europe"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 395260.0,
      "end_time": 399260.0,
      "text": "at the onset of World War I."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 399260.0,
      "end_time": 401260.0,
      "text": "So cyber weapons"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 401260.0,
      "end_time": 403260.0,
      "text": "are dangerous by nature,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 403260.0,
      "end_time": 406260.0,
      "text": "but in addition, they&#39;re emerging"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 406260.0,
      "end_time": 408260.0,
      "text": "in a much more unstable environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 408260.0,
      "end_time": 410260.0,
      "text": "If you remember the Cold War,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 410260.0,
      "end_time": 412260.0,
      "text": "it was a very hard game,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 412260.0,
      "end_time": 414260.0,
      "text": "but a stable one played only by two players,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 414260.0,
      "end_time": 416260.0,
      "text": "which allowed for some coordination between the two superpowers."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 417260.0,
      "end_time": 422260.0,
      "text": "Today we&#39;re moving to a multipolar world"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 422260.0,
      "end_time": 423260.0,
      "text": "in which coordination is much more complicated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 423260.0,
      "end_time": 426260.0,
      "text": "as we have seen at Copenhagen."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 426260.0,
      "end_time": 429260.0,
      "text": "And this coordination may become even trickier"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 429260.0,
      "end_time": 432260.0,
      "text": "with the introduction of cyber weapons."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 432260.0,
      "end_time": 434260.0,
      "text": "Why? Because no nation"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 434260.0,
      "end_time": 437260.0,
      "text": "knows for sure whether its neighbor"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 437260.0,
      "end_time": 439260.0,
      "text": "is about to attack."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 439260.0,
      "end_time": 441260.0,
      "text": "So nations may live under the threat"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 441260.0,
      "end_time": 444260.0,
      "text": "of what Nobel Prize winner Thomas Schelling"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 444260.0,
      "end_time": 446260.0,
      "text": "called the \"reciprocal fear of surprise attack,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 446260.0,
      "end_time": 448260.0,
      "text": "as I don&#39;t know if my neighbor"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 448260.0,
      "end_time": 450260.0,
      "text": "is about to attack me or not --"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 450260.0,
      "end_time": 452260.0,
      "text": "I may never know --"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 452260.0,
      "end_time": 454260.0,
      "text": "so I might take the upper hand"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 454260.0,
      "end_time": 457260.0,
      "text": "and attack first."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 457260.0,
      "end_time": 459260.0,
      "text": "Just last week,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 459260.0,
      "end_time": 463260.0,
      "text": "in a New York Times article dated January 26, 2010,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 463260.0,
      "end_time": 465260.0,
      "text": "it was revealed for the first time that"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 465260.0,
      "end_time": 468260.0,
      "text": "officials at the National Security Agency"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 468260.0,
      "end_time": 472260.0,
      "text": "were considering the possibility of preemptive attacks"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 472260.0,
      "end_time": 475260.0,
      "text": "in cases where the U.S. was about"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 475260.0,
      "end_time": 478260.0,
      "text": "to be cyberattacked."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 478260.0,
      "end_time": 480260.0,
      "text": "And these preemptive attacks"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 480260.0,
      "end_time": 481260.0,
      "text": "might not just remain"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 481260.0,
      "end_time": 484260.0,
      "text": "in cyberspace."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 485260.0,
      "end_time": 490260.0,
      "text": "In May 2009, General Kevin Chilton,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 490260.0,
      "end_time": 493260.0,
      "text": "commander of the U.S. nuclear forces,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 493260.0,
      "end_time": 498260.0,
      "text": "stated that in the event of cyberattacks against the U.S.,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 498260.0,
      "end_time": 501260.0,
      "text": "all options would be on the table."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 501260.0,
      "end_time": 503260.0,
      "text": "Cyber weapons do not replace"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 503260.0,
      "end_time": 505260.0,
      "text": "conventional or nuclear weapons --"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 505260.0,
      "end_time": 510260.0,
      "text": "they just add a new layer to the existing system of terror."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 510260.0,
      "end_time": 513260.0,
      "text": "But in doing so, they also add their own risk"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 513260.0,
      "end_time": 515260.0,
      "text": "of triggering a conflict --"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 515260.0,
      "end_time": 517260.0,
      "text": "as we&#39;ve just seen, a very important risk --"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 517260.0,
      "end_time": 519260.0,
      "text": "and a risk we may have to confront"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 519260.0,
      "end_time": 522260.0,
      "text": "with a collective security solution"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 522260.0,
      "end_time": 524260.0,
      "text": "which includes all of us:"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 524260.0,
      "end_time": 526260.0,
      "text": "European allies, NATO members,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 526260.0,
      "end_time": 528260.0,
      "text": "our American friends and allies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 528260.0,
      "end_time": 530260.0,
      "text": "our other Western allies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 530260.0,
      "end_time": 532260.0,
      "text": "and maybe, by forcing their hand a little,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 532260.0,
      "end_time": 535260.0,
      "text": "our Russian and Chinese partners."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 535260.0,
      "end_time": 537260.0,
      "text": "The information technologies"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 537260.0,
      "end_time": 538760.0,
      "text": "JoÃ«l de Rosnay was talking about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 538760.0,
      "end_time": 541260.0,
      "text": "which were historically born from military research,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 541260.0,
      "end_time": 543260.0,
      "text": "are today on the verge of developing"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 543260.0,
      "end_time": 546260.0,
      "text": "an offensive capability of destruction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 546260.0,
      "end_time": 550260.0,
      "text": "which could tomorrow, if we&#39;re not careful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 550260.0,
      "end_time": 553260.0,
      "text": "completely destroy world peace."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 553260.0,
      "end_time": 555260.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 555260.0,
      "end_time": 558260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}